#

Slow-Roasted Pork Belly with Apple Cider Caramel Glaze and Truffle Mashed Potatoes

$30
850 kcal
Difficulty: 70%

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

PaleoGluten-Free

Tags:

GourmetComfort FoodFall Flavors

Description

Succulent pork belly slow-roasted to perfection, glazed with a rich apple cider caramel and served with creamy truffle-infused mashed potatoes.

Ingredients

  • Pork Belly: 2 lbs
  • Apple Cider: 1 cup
  • Brown Sugar: 1/2 cup
  • Soy Sauce: 3 tbsp
  • Garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • Fresh Rosemary: 2 sprigs
  • Butter: 4 tbsp
  • Heavy Cream: 1/2 cup
  • Truffle Oil: 2 tbsp
  • Potatoes: 2 lbs
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
